description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the 'App' component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the root rendering using ReactDOM and wraps the application in React.StrictMode for highlighting potential problems.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to manage rendering of React components into a DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the DOM under the root.
